survey_response.review_text: He is a friend more than a doctor.Each time I meet him,he has made my day with his professional behaviour and his colgate smile. While doing his work he will keep you busy with his conversation and by the time you realise the job is done,which is the best thing in him. He is one of the best few doctors available in Bangalore....thank you sir.

From past 7 Years, we complete family going to this doctor.
First thing, the Doctor is ethical, professional and transparent.
He will not suggest any unnecessary treatments , unless and until patient requests for alternatives. He will always try to save the existing thing with best options.

Secondly, he is dexterous in his work. 

Ram Gopal

A soft-spoken gentleman, brilliant counselor and reasonable expertise in wisdom tooth extractions. I went there on Saturday and my wisdom tooth extraction was fixed on Sunday. It was a three minute process. No pain. Even the anasthesia injection admission did not hurt. A well maintained clinic. Above all his charisma as a brilliant counselor stands him out from the rest of the crowd.

I visited Dr. Chandrashekar for routine checkup and to fix all possible issues as I had not visited dentist for a long time. Dr was very courteous and explained me patiently about issues. He not only made me comfortable but explained issues in gentle manner . he was very professional in his approach and discussion with him was very reassuring. He also gave me tips on how to maintain healthy tooth. Overall I had great experience.

review_reply.reply_text: The cleaning of your teeth was done slowly and methodically keeping in mind your sensitive teeth. We have treated you with utmost empathy and patience as we do with all our patients. If you had visited or reached out to us again we would have prescribed you appropriate medication for your increased sensitivity.
